1545:Generated_Source\PSoC5/ADC_DelSig_1.c **** *  and ADC_DelSig_1_StartConvert() to restart the conversion.
1546:Generated_Source\PSoC5/ADC_DelSig_1.c **** *
1547:Generated_Source\PSoC5/ADC_DelSig_1.c **** * Parameters:
1548:Generated_Source\PSoC5/ADC_DelSig_1.c **** *  config:  configuration user wants to select.
1549:Generated_Source\PSoC5/ADC_DelSig_1.c **** *           Valid range: 1..4
1550:Generated_Source\PSoC5/ADC_DelSig_1.c **** *  restart:  Restart option. 1 means start the ADC and restart the conversion.
1551:Generated_Source\PSoC5/ADC_DelSig_1.c **** *                            0 means do not start the ADC and conversion.
1552:Generated_Source\PSoC5/ADC_DelSig_1.c **** *
1553:Generated_Source\PSoC5/ADC_DelSig_1.c **** * Return:
